{
  "stem": "7093.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wasn't-- I, I was taken-- I mean, I went with the troops, with the prisoners of war and with my fiance slowly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It took us about three-and-a-half weeks to get through France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Wherever we went, we got lots of money, lots of clothing, especially I got lots of things because I was from camps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The others were prisoners of war with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I, I, I was a woman with all men, really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, and they were incredibly generous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And eventually, we arrived in Toulon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We spent-- to show that how, how my, my memory was bad, we spent three days in Paris.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I didn't remember that I had an uncle there, whom I adored, by the way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I had no idea that I had an uncle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Later on, when I returned to Paris I found out that I was one street away from him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And anyway, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And by the time I arrived in-- well, in Toulon, we were received, first, by the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they interviewed us and examined us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then they-- then they, they told this man that he can go home to his mother, I mean, to his home, and he-- and take me, of course.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because he guaranteed-- that everywhere he wrote, he signed that I am his fiancee and that I am coming with him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I had no number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I, I grew bigger and bigger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I was 39 kilogram when I collapsed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And now I was growing bigger and bigger until I went up to 98 kilogram.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because, no, it turned out that it was a so-called something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In French, they call it [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have no idea what-- it's some anemia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, I had heart trouble.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
